quran[16]{c,v,t}:
  38,1,"Sād. By the Qur’an, full of reminder"
  38,2,yet those who disbelieve are in arrogance and dissension
  38,3,How many generations We destroyed before them; they cried out when it was too late for deliverance
  38,4,"They wonder that a warner has come to them from among themselves, and the disbelievers say, “This is a magician and a liar"
  38,5,"Has he made all gods into one God? Indeed, this is something strange!”"
  38,6,"The leaders among them departed, saying, “Carry on as you are, and stay faithful to your gods. Indeed, there is a motive behind it"
  38,7,We have not heard of this in the last religion. This is nothing but a fabrication
  38,8,"Has the Reminder been sent down to him from among us?” Rather, they are in doubt about My Reminder, for they have not yet tasted My punishment"
  38,9,"Or do they possess the treasuries of the mercy of your Lord, the All-Mighty, the Bestower"
  38,10,Or do they have the dominion of the heavens and earth and all that is between them? Then let them ascend by any means
  38,11,This is only a small army among several armies that will soon be defeated
  38,12,"Before them, the people of Noah, ‘Ād, and mighty Pharaoh rejected [their prophets]"
  38,13,"and Thamūd and the people of Lot, and the dwellers of the Forest – such were the [denier] parties"
  38,14,"Each of them rejected their messenger, therefore My punishment became inevitable"
  38,15,They are only waiting for a single Blast that cannot be stopped
  38,16,"They say, “Our Lord, hasten for us our share [of punishment] before the Day of Reckoning.”"